profile:
Save thousands by dealing directly with a manufacturer! Canadian Choice Windows and Doors Inc. is a leading manufacturer of windows in Canada, serving Ontario. Canadian Choice Windows and Doors offers a huge selection of replacement windows including energy efficient windows, vinyl windows, casement windows, awning windows and bow and bay windows.

Canadian Choice Windows and Doors has been serving Toronto, Richmond Hill, North York, Markham, Mississauga, Oakville, Burlington, Hamilton, Kitchener, Cambridge, Niagra Falls and the surrounding areas as well as in Calgary, Edmonton, Winnipeg and Northern Ontario. 

Why is Canadian Choice Windows and Doors your best solution for window replacement?

1. No Pressure Estimate: take your time & make informed decision

2. Save Money: Energy Star windows will reduce your energy bill by 30 %

3. Professional Installation: flawless installation and thorough clean up by courteous installers

4. High Quality: The highest quality windows in the industry, featuring foam injected honey comb structure.
 
5. Easy Financing: Financing solutions to fit anyone’s lifestyle

6. Maximum Comfort: low-E coating to reflect summer sun and retain winter heat with our Cardinal Smart Glass system.

7. Zero Maintenance: our windows are easy to clean from within the home and will never fade or discolor

Canadian Choice Windows and Doors is your smartest solution for window and door replacement.

profile:
Understanding clients’ needs and providing them with outstanding customer service is the cornerstone of Naturally Gas Limited.

Since 1988, owners Kevin & Lisa Smith have been keeping families and businesses comfortable all year long. Specializing in the sales, installation and servicing of everything from furnaces and central air conditioning to fireplaces, Naturally Gas Limited has earned a reputation for honest, reliable service.

Customers who call will always speak to the owner or a live person...not a machine. A refreshing change of pace in today's ever-growing impersonal business environment.

Naturally Gas Limited—Treating customers the way we would like to be treated.

After hours available for emergencies only!

At HVAC Grimsby for Heating & Air Conditioning, we take great pride in providing effective solutions to all our clients. Supplying indoor spaces with the best air quality and comfort is what we aim for.

Our company provides ventilation, heating, and air conditioning services in Grimsby. Our team of technicians is fully qualified to assist you in picking the system that best fits your space as well as your budget. Whether you need furnace repair, AC repair, water heater replacement, AC maintenance, vent cleaner installation, or anything HVAC related, we got your back.

profile: We are a locally owned and operated business serving both residential and commercial customers in the Grimsby, Hamilton area. At BAM Mechanical Services Inc., we strive to provide the highest degree of quality service and efficiency. Our goal is to create lasting relationship with our customers built on trust and workmanship. Our owner has over 15 years experience in a wide range of projects and unique customers needs. We offer value by providing top notch services at competitive prices. The company's main values are trust, efficiency, attention to deal, local, and quality. What we offer is a one stop shop, we can service a wide range of equipment and can meet our customers needs whether it be for their personal, rental or business space. We operate largely with repeat customers because we offer trusted service with a personalized approach.
